description: This stunning, sun-soaked 2-bedroom, 2-bathroom condo offers expansive windows, soaring 12-foot ceilings, and an OFF STREET PARKING SPACE! The open-concept floor plan features hardwood floors, a spacious kitchen with granite countertops, maple cabinetry, and stainless-steel appliances, plus a separate dining area. Step out onto the fabulous East-facing deck, accessible from the living space, providing a serene outdoor retreat. Convenient amenities include an in-unit washer/dryer, central air conditioning, a dedicated storage unit and a professionally managed building. Located in the coveted City Point neighborhood of South Boston, this bright, airy home is just blocks from M & N Street beaches, shops, dining, and the East Broadway commercial district. The charming boutique brick building offers a common garden and two guest parking spots, including overnight accommodations. Don’t miss your chance to view this gem in person!
